feature_bullets: The RCA cable coming with backup camera is 19.5ft, if you want to install the rear camera on a large vehicle such as SUV RV Pickup Truck, a longer RCA extension cable is required.

RCA Video Cable Compatible with Professional CCTV / surveillance camera, front / rear view camera, DVD Dash, Head Unit, car stereo, parking monitor display, TV box with yellow RCA connector, and so on.
RCA Video Cable Weatherproof for outdoor use,100% shielded offering superb protection against EMI/ RFI interference.
RCA Video Cable Comes with RCA Video Female to Female Coupler and Power Cable.
